character_name: Ernst Stavro Blofeld: The head of SPECTRE and Bond's arch-enemy. Gray had previously appeared in the series when he played Dikko Henderson in 1967's You Only Live Twice.
Plenty O'Toole: A woman Bond meets at a casino.
Albert R. 'Bert' Saxby: Whyte's casino manager who is in cahoots with Blofeld. His name is a reference to the producer Albert R. Broccoli.[4][5]
Mr. Wint and Mr. Kidd: Blofeld's henchmen.
Dr. Metz: A scientist who is the world's leading expert on laser refraction
Q: Head of MI6's technical department.
Shady Tree: A stand-up comedian and smuggler.
Peter Franks: A diamond smuggler whose identity is taken by Bond.
Sir Donald Munger: A diamond expert who brings the case to MI6.
Morton Slumber: President of Slumber Incorporated
